    <section class="use-cases" id="use-cases" data-home-module="aapanel_use_cases">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header anim-in"><h2>Powering Every Use Case</h2><p class="sub">From personal blogs to enterprise clusters — aaPanel scales with your ambition.</p><div class="line"></div></div>
            <div class="uc-grid-v3 anim-in d1">

                <!-- 01 -->
                <div class="uc-card-v3">
                    <div class="uc-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 014 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 014-10z"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Rapid Deployment of Personal Blogs or Websites</h3>
                    <p class="uc-v3-desc">This is the most common use case. You can use the "One-Click Deployment" feature to install environments for WordPress, Typecho, or Hexo in just a few minutes.</p>
                    <div class="uc-v3-core">Eliminates the tedious process of manually configuring Nginx/Apache, MySQL, and PHP.</div>
                </div>

                <!-- 02 -->
                <div class="uc-card-v3">
                    <div class="uc-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Building High-Performance Production Development Environments</h3>
                    <p class="uc-v3-desc">Using the "App Store" within the panel, you can quickly switch between multiple versions of programming languages such as PHP, Python, Node.js, and Go.</p>
                    <div class="uc-v3-core">Convenient for developers to configure differentiated runtime environments for various projects on the same server.</div>
                </div>

                <!-- 03 -->
                <div class="uc-card-v3">
                    <div class="uc-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/><rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6"/><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Multi-Site Hosting for SMEs (Virtual Hosting)</h3>
                    <p class="uc-v3-desc">For small businesses with multiple business lines, aaPanel makes it easy to isolate files and databases for different websites.</p>
                    <div class="uc-v3-core">Centralized management for multiple domains, one-click SSL certificate configuration (Let's Encrypt), and simplified security management.</div>
                </div>

                <!-- 04 -->
                <div class="uc-card-v3">
                    <div class="uc-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Automated Backup and Disaster Recovery</h3>
                    <p class="uc-v3-desc">The panel includes comprehensive backup scheduling, supporting synchronization of site data and databases to local disks, FTP, or cloud storage (e.g., AWS S3, Google Cloud Storage).</p>
                    <div class="uc-v3-core">Enables off-site disaster recovery and one-click restoration, minimizing downtime risks.</div>
                </div>

                <!-- 05 -->
                <div class="uc-card-v3">
                    <div class="uc-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3"/><path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Efficient Visual Database Management</h3>
                    <p class="uc-v3-desc">aaPanel integrates phpMyAdmin by default, supporting SQL queries, data imports/exports, and table optimization directly through the web browser.</p>
                    <div class="uc-v3-core">Allows for complex database operations without needing local database clients (like Navicat).</div>
                </div>

                <!-- 06 -->
                <div class="uc-card-v3">
                    <div class="uc-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="M7 16l4-8 4 4 4-6"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Real-Time Server Performance Monitoring and Alerts</h3>
                    <p class="uc-v3-desc">Using the built-in monitoring dashboard, you can view CPU, RAM, disk I/O, and bandwidth usage in real-time, and set up email or SMS notifications for high-load events.</p>
                    <div class="uc-v3-core">Helps identify resource bottlenecks or traffic anomalies caused by attacks (such as CC attacks) in a timely manner.</div>
                </div>

                <!-- 07 -->
                <div class="uc-card-v3">
                    <div class="uc-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5l2 3h9a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Cloud-Style File System Management</h3>
                    <p class="uc-v3-desc">The built-in file manager provides an interface similar to a desktop file explorer, supporting online code editing, file compression/extraction, and permission management.</p>
                    <div class="uc-v3-core">Allows for easy modification of configuration files or uploading of static resources without needing an SSH client.</div>
                </div>

                <!-- 08 -->
                <div class="uc-card-v3">
                    <div class="uc-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Security Firewall and Anti-Malicious Access</h3>
                    <p class="uc-v3-desc">aaPanel provides basic firewall configuration, allowing you to block malicious IPs and restrict port access with one click. You can also deploy professional WAF (Web Application Firewall) plugins to defend against SQL injection and XSS attacks.</p>
                    <div class="uc-v3-core">Provides a graphical security hardening solution, reducing the risk of server intrusion.</div>
                </div>

                <!-- 09 -->
                <div class="uc-card-v3">
                    <div class="uc-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg></div>
                    <h3>Docker Management (Beginner-Friendly)</h3>
                    <p class="uc-v3-desc">For advanced users, the panel includes a Docker management interface. You don't need to memorize complex docker run commands; you can manage container lifecycles, view logs, and pull images directly from the web interface.</p>
                    <div class="uc-v3-core">Lowers the barrier to entry for containerization, helping users smoothly migrate to container-based architectures.</div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

